{"name":"Mark Iron","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"Vanguards, IronVale","alignment":"Neutral Good","hitDice":"15","armorName":"other","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"18 (Energy Shield)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"82 (15d8 + 15)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"8","dexPoints":"18","conPoints":"12","intPoints":"20","wisPoints":"16","chaPoints":"10","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"7","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Chronolens","desc":"[MON] directly uses power from the Chronolens to control Time and Space. This starts with 8 charges (YottaWatt of power), and regains 1 per turn."},{"name":"Legendary Resistance","desc":"If [MON] fails a saving throw, he can use a charge to succeed instead."},{"name":"Temporal Awareness","desc":"[MON] gains +10 to initiative."},{"name":"Energy Shield","desc":"[MON] has an arcane-ward like Energy Shield that absorbs a max of 20HP of damage. This regains 10HP every time he expends a charge."},{"name":"The Dark Side of the Force","desc":"[MON]'s energy shields take 4x amount of Force Damage."},{"name":"Tesseract","desc":"[MON] can freely travel between interstitial space (or time). [MON] can create projections of himself anywhere on Epis."}],"actions":[{"name":"Plasma Pistol","desc":"[MON] fires at someone with a pistol. [INT ATK + 1] to hit, range 60/120 ft. _Hit:_ [INT 2D6] force damage. Alternatively, he can cast shield on himself or an ally within 60ft."},{"name":"Force Field","desc":"[MON] creates a 10ft. radius force field that prevents all allies from taking damage. This force field has 25HP."},{"name":"Firewall","desc":"[MON] summons a 5x30x60 digital wall that prevents all projectiles or creatures from passing through within 30ft. This firewall has 25HP."},{"name":"Time Ravage","desc":"[MON] expends 4 charges and shatters the very fabric of reality. He can summon 3 Vanguards of his choice from before the Void fight. Once a Vanguard dies, it can't be re-summoned again."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Banishment","desc":"Once per day, [MON] consumes 4 charges to banish up to 2 creatures from interstitial space."},{"name":"Radar Scanner","desc":"[MON] reveals all invisible or disguised entities within a 60ft radius."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Temporal Rewind","desc":"[MON] expends a charge, rewinds time, and cancel an action. The target creature keeps their action but loses the resources needed (ie. spell slots)."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"int","order":3},{"name":"wis","order":4}],"skills":[{"name":"arcana","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"history","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"investigation","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Mark","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":6,"damage":[]}